{"title":"诗二首","authors":["樊忠慰"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":1,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樊忠慰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情醉了溪水和田园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛙鸣叫颤茅屋的星天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当阳光点燃大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头和游子也温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕牛的汗珠湿了梯田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农人的脊梁金灿灿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁的一生让勤劳丰满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿不着肚子，披不完布衫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几捆干柴，半筐猪草，一把弯镰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割痛少年的夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有人娶走流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有人嫁给青山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年了，放牛娃竹笛横吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暖了村姑和夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风刮过多情的山岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗吠瘦了红豆的家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金片的阳光，洒下潺潺的流淌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的月色，穿上树林的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是个路人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉睡在你颤抖的鸡鸣和花香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温馨童话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把霞彩逼到皮肤上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女的脸颊像羞涩的花园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋下春天和花香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体淌清泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼底飘阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起素手，白银变金黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地放飞彩蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵呼吸月色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海的丝绸缀满星光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘一朵野花，打开爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住进永不凋谢的家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘑菇房是蚂蚁温馨的童话"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}